name: Adventure Time Princess Pack
description:
Support me on Ko-Fi!

C'mon, grab your friends!

I wanted to try making a LORA with multiple concepts this time. There are 9 subjects here:

  • Princess Bubblegum

  • Marceline

  • Flame Princess

  • Breakfast Princess

  • Jungle Princess

  • Doctor Princess

  • Ice Queen

  • Huntress Wizard

  • Lumpy Space Princess

It's pretty reliable at telling them apart, but you may need to explicitly mention features like skin color or accessories sometimes to push it in the right direction, especially if you mention more than one character.
